I know good vietnamese food... I grew up in San Jose, essentially vietnamese central of the SF Bay Area... this is now my go to place in Downtown Phoenix. The prices are super reasonable... like for 2 spring rolls its $2.50... Pho Bowls are around $6 to 48. For my girlfriend and myself the bill came out to $25. Not too bad.... the customer service is real great too!

